Title: Night Sky Observing
Book Description: Join Bob Trembley to observe what the late spring night sky has to offer!

Title: Solar Observing
Book Description: Join Bob Trembley to observe the closest star- the Sun!

Title: Walk the Solar System
Book Description: Stretched down the longest hall of the hotel- is a scale-model of the solar system. At the position of the Sun and orbits of the planets- you will find a plaque (with a QR code) with more information on that body.
